### --- Create Hole 44 event source ---
# Links the venue to the Hole44WebsiteImporter.
# The sourceType "HOLE44" matches EventSource.HOLE44.
# The URL is the `/events/` listing (overview); the scraper fetches each
# `/event/<date-slug>/` detail page internally for promoter, doors, and image.
